講<br />\n千祈唔好因為呢d事嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:16:55.000Z","msg":"13:27<br />\n我慢慢推"},{"pid":"4e6291ba25dd9f8704d89406ca9368170a02df3b","tid":1589352,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"929 connect咗好多國家, 一定要集中<br />\n<br />\n101 就參考慮返805, 遍地開花"},{"pid":"d7c575daf37342c6cc603e9ed2b488e76c22d08f","tid":1589352,"uid":201170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"開花啦"},{"pid":"1104dc25f2604b5668dd217e30ed8f7f8578bdf0","tid":1589352,"uid":306748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"有929集中一區已經夠晒，101唔使再重覆，可以5-7區開花，要營造全香港每區嘅人都反共嘅畫面。<br />\n人數方面，一區一百萬人，同五區每區20萬人，其實咪一撚樣。同埋集中會俾圍捕嘅風險高，啲人反而唔夠膽出來，我有幾個朋友915就係因為咁無出。同<br />\n埋住得遠個啲驚無車走會好早散<br />\n<br />\n最重要反而係每區要搵定一兩個目標搞9佢"},{"pid":"b668bffed2b40acd2f7c51d7b598d83862dd3e02","tid":1589352,"uid":291426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c699b6e590603110db282f805e89d627905b6617","tid":1589352,"uid":124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:06:33.000Z","msg":"集中好難多人出啦<br />\n上次遊行有眼見 <br />\n5點就停港鐵 周圍都係POPO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"P牌無得投所以寫出黎<br />\n<br />\n我算係和理非。每次金鐘遊行我都有出，但係地區遊行就唔係次次都會。<br />\n<br />\n我想講，如果係分開十八區，我好大機會唔會出去或者停留好短時間。<br />\n<br />\n就算915佢咁早封站都清場，我都覺得唔太擔心，因為銅鑼灣太多普通人同好多地方去，換左衫已經唔洗驚（身上只有口罩gear）。<br />\n<br />\n但係地區遊行人數真係少過港島好多，而且又唔係個個區咁四通八達，一埋牙就好易變左前線。好老實我係驚既<br />\n<br />\n而且其他區未必有政府建築物，無乜象徵意義，好似無目標咁"},{"pid":"198c4e5d52191b01f4e0f3c44aeebe9677b163ea","tid":1589352,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"15:36"},{"pid":"16e83832c894bd5bd2bfb0d80268466b70b4881a","tid":1589352,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:25:37.000Z","msg":"集中先唔講出唔出到 就算比你出到 要走都好難<br />\n開花啦"},{"pid":"94cb7ff2e2a0a605f9b3c968b7bfe97c1d19cbfc","tid":1589352,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"唔好再呃自己<br />\n民陣遊行一定唔批,<br />\n黨鐵一定會封,<br />\n出唔出到黎都成問題, 黎到都走唔到, <br />\n你諗下大西北班手足<br />\n<br />\n所以一定遍地開花"},{"pid":"1b98e0acd051c820a485ae99c74b0ba44fe5dd87","tid":1589352,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2783aa46eea923cbb3c8d741779a6afedf01d0e7","tid":1589352,"uid":261740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"大家慢慢講<br />\n千祈唔好因為呢d事嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"其實都要做定文宣, 得返一個星期"},{"pid":"8e2a5255d47ef9c4a4fd745d729f0898a423d791","tid":1589352,"uid":325214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"比較傾向 遍地<br />\n集中的話 一停黨鐵就圍捕"},{"pid":"1ac6bf6b1ced7c657865913e5ce7daf3a1707916","tid":1589352,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:29:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"660cc72ef86b74c19fda9b14e51289f4d19d0bcd","tid":1589352,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b98e0acd051c820a485ae99c74b0ba44fe5dd87","tid":1589352,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2783aa46eea923cbb3c8d741779a6afedf01d0e7","tid":1589352,"uid":261740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"大家慢慢講<br />\n千祈唔好因為呢d事嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"其實都要做定文宣, 得返一個星期